sequenceDiagram
    participant Input as StreamChunk
    participant Exec as OverWindowExecutor
    participant MLC as ManagedLruCache<OwnedRow, PartitionCache>
    participant PC as PartitionCache (per partition)
    participant ST as StateTable (Hummock/Storage)

    Input->>Exec: Provide Chunk of Records

    loop For each Partition in Chunk
        Exec->>Exec: Extract Partition Key
        Exec->>MLC: contains(partition_key)?

        alt Cache Miss
            MLC-->>Exec: False
            Exec->>MLC: put(partition_key, new PartitionCache())
        else Cache Hit
            MLC-->>Exec: True
        end

        Exec->>MLC: get_mut(partition_key)
        MLC-->>Exec: Return PartitionCache reference

        Exec->>PC: build_changes(delta)

        alt Row in PartitionCache
            PC-->>Exec: Return Cached Row
        else Row not in PartitionCache
            PC->>ST: Get row from state table
            ST-->>PC: Return row
            PC->>PC: Update internal range cache
        end

        Exec->>Exec: Compute Window Function Results
        Exec->>ST: write_record(updated_row)
        Exec->>PC: update_cache(updated_row)
    end

    Note over Exec,MLC: On Barrier/Commit
    Exec->>MLC: evict() -> removes epochs < watermark
